      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       qry-rou-pri-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione flag di uscita                  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-cnt-qry-rou-pri      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Determinazione function-keys in Mark-points     *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   qry-det-fky-000      thru qry-det-fky-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
